sql:
SELECT intersection_name, number_of_lanes
FROM intersections
ORDER BY number_of_lanes DESC;

external_knowledge:
High congestion level typically refers to a condition where the traffic volume approaches or exceeds the road capacity, leading to slow speeds and increased travel times; 
Top 5 most congested traffic data means the 5 traffic records with the highest total vehicles for each intersection; 
Intersections with traffic lights are those having a physical signal controlling the flow of traffic.
